Value: Winsome Resources Limited focuses on exploring lithium projects in Canada. It holds an option to acquire an interest in the projects, including Cancet project, which comprises 395 claims; Adina project comprising 57 claims; and Sirmac-Clapier project comprising 77 claims located in Quebec, Canada. The company was incorporated in 2021 and is headquartered in West Perth, Australia. Winsome Resources Limited is a subsidiary of MetalsTech Limited.
